## Kit Setup (for agents)

To set up agentic-kit in a project, run:

```bash
.agentic-kit/init.sh --non-interactive --ide=cursor   # or --ide=claude / --ide=both
```

When `--yes` is used, the script will output a `[AGENT ACTION REQUIRED]` block.
**After the script exits, fill in `PROJECT.md` yourself:**
inspect the project files (`package.json`, `pyproject.toml`, `Cargo.toml`, `go.mod`, `Makefile`, version files, etc.) and replace every `<placeholder>` with the correct value.
Then run `.agentic-kit/tools/validate-config.sh` to confirm all placeholders are resolved.

